dataset.title: Nomenclatural Validation Of Ichthyosaura Alpestris Bakonyiensis Subsp. N. (Amphibia: Salamandridae) From Western Hungary

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Vörös, Judit (2022): Nomenclatural Validation Of Ichthyosaura Alpestris Bakonyiensis Subsp. N. (Amphibia: Salamandridae) From Western Hungary. Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae 68 (4): 393-394, DOI: 10.17109/AZH.68.4.393.2022, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.17109/azh.68.4.393.2022
